<br>
The following screenshots were taken at some occasions I will explain now.<br>
I always get these really really bad bugs when I do or have one of the following things:<br>
<br>
- Fight<br>
- Stand on someones corpse (or a mobs corpse)<br>
- Someone is very close to my char<br>
<br>
At that point, some parts, up to the whole screen get buggy like mad, until I either move away or stop fighting (when I fight its always when I have my hands with shield or sword in front of me, so again, very close to me).<br>
<br>
It looks to me as if it would be those 'space filler' you may know when you have very low Clipplane and look down a mountain. You will then at the points where you dont see anything anymore, have strange grafics with small parts of the zone just where you still see somehting (I hope you get what I mean).<br>
<br>
The buggy spaces always have the color of my weapon/shield/armor or the corpses or persons colors/textures.<br>
<br>
I reinstalled my grafic card, downloaded new drivers (ATI Radeon 7500), I reinstalled the Luclin Patch - since it happened llike 1 hour after I entered the game after the patch.<br>
Nothin helps. Noone seems to have this and noone seems to be able to help me.<br>
<br>
If you have ANY idea what could solve my problem, please let me know.<br>
When you have a 24dly sword and a shield and you have this bug, you really freak out to see your screen go nuts twice a second. After 5 minutes you're about to freak, I tell yas.<br>
